## üìê Architecture Overview

### Site Structure
This is a **Jekyll-based static site** with the following architecture:

- **Single-page application** using panel-based navigation with anchor links (`#work`, `#360lens`, etc.)
- **Collection-based content management** via Jekyll collections (`_projects`, `_posts`)
- **Netlify CMS integration** for non-technical content editing
- **Dark mode support** with theme persistence via localStorage
- **Client-side filtering & search** for project discovery

